pc2.ex
Class ContestInfo

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--pc2.ex.ContestInfo
public class ContestInfo
extends java.lang.Object

General Contest info, used by PC2 Clients

This class should not be used directly, instead use on of the abstract classes or BaseClient to retrieve values/settings.
